Only one man Lieutenant Thomas Brightwater - now fully aware of the horrifying truth of Doe's origins - seems willing to shift the course of a fate that may generate an even darker reality should shadowy imperial forces have their way. But buried deep in the bowels of an off the grid rural Sudanese military base, and facing off against a strike force determined to exterminate Doe at all costs, Lt.
